Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.83,0:23:23.29,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}做想做的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:50.02,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}三姐妹的雲雨陰晴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:52.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（還是夏天的時候…）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.74,0:01:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上學去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:01:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.77,0:02:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  為什麼只有春香臨時放假
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.01,0:02:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐一向很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是校方的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.24,0:02:11.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  是校方的照顧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.34,0:02:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者說是國家政策
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  原來是國家政策啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.67,0:02:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要洗的衣物都洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.28,0:02:30.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大清早的就這麼無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後要幹點什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在春香正悠閒地喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.93,0:02:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:07.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼好的天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久就能晾乾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.68,0:03:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒什麼要清洗的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全無事可做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:29.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在春香姐姐正悠閒地歇著的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:32.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請過得自在些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天開始又是平日的生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使只有今天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也還請好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.98,0:03:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到一個人會這麼無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.63,0:03:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就該出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做些點心吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.41,0:03:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒替我準備甜甜的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:03:59.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這口氣我絕對嚥不下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子你也這麼想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.54,0:04:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:16.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閒來無事居然做了這麼大一個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來好像還沒吃午飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請過得愉快些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必惦記著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  南同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你提著水桶站一邊去就行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且得是有好多奶油的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然這口氣我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:51.01,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（注：原文“腹の虫が収まらない”，此处亦可解作蛔虫之类）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這口氣！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這口氣…給我等著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.12,0:05:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.22,0:05:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的那份呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,0:05:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:22.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少給我裝蒜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你嘴邊不還掛著好多奶油嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜甜的蛋糕  都叫你給吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:35.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐幸福的假日就全完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很明顯她是吃了些什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,0:05:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:44.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我怎麼冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\fsp130}　{\fsp1}Shaving Foam{\r}\N那怎麼看都是修面泡沫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就體諒她一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.53,0:05:59.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒弄清楚就發脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.70,0:06:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是鬍鬚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也差不多是長的年齡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:13.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我一大早的就得忍受妹妹的摧殘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你自己不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為早飯已經做好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再睡下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睫毛會絞在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛就再也睜不開了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不謝我  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐  今天我來幫忙準備晚飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼做些什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋你這丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非得讓你早上起不來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:07:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就換我騎你身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:31.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱倆暢談到天亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說要什麼到天亮？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直說我是蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但真實的想法是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱倆好好聊到天亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.46,0:07:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:08:00.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這確實是我設想不周到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有解釋清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這白癡的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.04,0:08:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直讓我想洋洋灑灑地罵個痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.56,0:08:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是無奈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的舌頭轉不了那麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓人焦心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還有很多想說的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只好在「蠢貨」這句話中寄托自己的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:28.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這樣一來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.68,0:08:33.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又無從知道自己到底蠢在什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:35.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可能的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真想寫一份卷帙浩繁的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.96,0:08:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳細論述你究竟蠢在什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:43.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是無奈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:46.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有這麼閒得無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.20,0:08:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我這妹妹真不中用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.99,0:08:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:54.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:08:59.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.94,0:09:01.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我裝什麼裝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.99,0:09:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這在一旁聽你口若懸河的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舌頭不是挺靈活嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要煩請你繼續了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.16,0:09:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我並不是說你智商低
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:23.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為博得周圍的歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扮演著專家級白癡的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.79,0:09:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都在想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.57,0:09:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實腦子不靈光是演不好白癡的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  確實是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.53,0:09:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一直在想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我犯下了什麼惡行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼非得受這份罪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  看起來很困的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  被你看穿了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:09:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:02.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四個小時之前我就困了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好久沒聊這麼盡興了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得有些口渴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可樂和橙汁  你要哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要可樂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是碳酸飲料我可撐不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.49,0:10:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝完了別忘記刷牙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不想得蟲牙對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.91,0:10:32.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:37.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在幾點了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三點的下午茶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.03,0:11:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒你倆的份
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:13.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（下一個週六）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:28.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（蠢貨考察報告①  南千秋）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.45,0:11:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就你的白癡水準的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嘗試著寫了一份卷帙浩繁的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就好好地讀到天亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.49,0:11:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地反省
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:04.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈她發燒了  躺床上休息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.73,0:12:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？是感冒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:14.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.52,0:12:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.25,0:12:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:25.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:27.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想脫掉一件衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.58,0:12:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後又覺得很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天到底是什麼天氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.12,0:12:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.35,0:12:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  公車來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面寫著「途徑南家  開往黃泉」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開往黃泉？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要上車
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別上去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感到那公車很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:52.98,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（問診）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.42,0:12:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前陣子是我吃了你的冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.53,0:12:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼想說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.91,0:13:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她居然不生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:04.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來真是病得不輕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.02,0:13:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天也把你的冰淇淋給吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然對病人動手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:14.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（治療）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:17.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千…千秋？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡也會得感冒  真是不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:21.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（注：语出日谚“馬鹿は風邪を引かない”）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:25.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡正是因為不會照顧自己才會得感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣我都是白癡是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.13,0:13:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧走著瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我瞬間擺平這病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要擰著你那張臉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.43,0:13:47.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼你說對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好期待著我的復活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:03.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發脾氣的話會燒得更厲害的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.85,0:14:07.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.27,0:14:11.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了  不用一直守著我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要播你喜歡的節目了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視節目無所謂的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著你在這兒受苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比看電視有趣多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說「對不起」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:36.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說「對不起」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:44.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.18,0:14:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的病好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:14:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擰得太使勁了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.37,0:15:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吃蘋果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:07.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.02,0:15:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒精神到能一口氣吞下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.46,0:15:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  還有剩菜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\fsp1}Piment{\fsp369}　{\r}\N不吃柿子椒和胡蘿蔔這些對身體有好處的東西可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:29.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種深色的蔬菜還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子真是  嘗都不嘗就說不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:35.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可是長不大的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你腦瓜不發育是因為什麼樣的偏食？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:46.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都別鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.79,0:15:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個  待會兒我要去洗衣店
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:15:56.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把校服拿出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我可以穿一下你的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:10.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別光在一旁看著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.41,0:16:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也來幫幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.91,0:16:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只差一點就可以穿進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  剛才「哧」的一聲…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我脫下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋你穿上試試
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐的校服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我可以穿夏奈的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.20,0:16:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人懷念呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿倒是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過記得在撐破之前脫下來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  你知道怎麼系領帶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.38,0:16:54.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:56.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種玩意就隨便對付一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.59,0:17:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼覺得完全不靠譜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你自己系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.60,0:17:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.64,0:17:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好夏奈挺苗條的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是嗎  是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.17,0:17:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差一點就穿不進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼想說的就說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好夏奈挺苗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部很緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就直說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我不給你點苦頭嘗嘗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  浴室打掃乾淨了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋正在同黃綠色的蔬菜抗爭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.67,0:17:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡蘿蔔  柿子椒和韭菜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.48,0:17:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時和三種蔬菜抗爭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.03,0:18:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,減油！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.07,0:18:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是替她加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬆垮跨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正合適
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混賬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\fsp55}　{\fsp1}Cheese Lemon Custard Chiffon Pie{\r}\N我想吃奶酪檸檬蛋糕酥餡餅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:40.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香肯不肯做給我吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.54,0:18:44.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近儘是甜食  恐怕不肯做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:49.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許我把材料準備好她就肯做了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.68,0:18:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這也不能保證她會立即做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:05.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香要傍晚才回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:10.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間我們來做些點心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.80,0:19:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點心？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶酪檸檬蛋糕酥餡餅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.36,0:19:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餡餅？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.56,0:19:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們來說太困難了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.41,0:19:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等春香姐姐回來了讓她幫你做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是春香說想吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:28.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了感謝她平日對我們的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:30.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替她做一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得不好也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  重要的是心意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  千秋沒必要做好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要看見她那份熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香就會再做給我們的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你剛才…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.66,0:19:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這輩子頭一回說了句像樣的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.24,0:19:56.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫頭一回？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.74,0:19:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說過好幾回了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.28,0:20:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那麼千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.17,0:20:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開工了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦—！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做成了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:14.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？做成了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別從頭到尾都在一邊偷懶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.12,0:20:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我來試試味兒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.86,0:20:24.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的得意之作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  得把廚房收拾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.53,0:20:33.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是想吃的人是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.19,0:20:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？好甜的味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:46.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了春香姐姐想吃的奶酪檸酥蛋糕檬餡餅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.94,0:20:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？檸酥？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.00,0:20:51.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過我想吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.33,0:21:01.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.50,0:21:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋酪檸酥奶糕檬餡餅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:07.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是咱倆合作的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.61,0:21:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也得試試味兒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.03,0:21:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.96,0:21:13.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這味道可以拿得出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.23,0:21:15.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼拿出手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.23,0:21:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好容易可以讓一直照顧我們的春香姐姐嘗嘗的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.43,0:21:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:24.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你們倆的心意就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.14,0:21:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  你這人真是好得讓我討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是更讓人討厭的傢伙是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.95,0:21:41.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管揍我吧  到你消氣為止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.27,0:21:43.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰怕誰  你這蠢貨！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:44.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.62,0:21:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  算了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  她都哭起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.96,0:21:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱們一起再做一份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.01,0:21:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.13,0:21:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.03,0:23:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.32,0:23:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我想給你介紹一位男生…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.31,0:23:34.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.91,0:23:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.63,0:23:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩X女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.57,0:23:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便一提
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.56,0:23:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次他將是我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.69,0:23:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  姐姐有些弄不明白…

